    <lb n="31" rend="perpendicular"/> <choice><corr>ἐνδείξασθε</corr><sic>ενδιξασθε</sic></choice> οὖν τὴν ἔμφυτον ὑμῶν ἀγάπην καὶ <choice><corr>εὐσπ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">λ</supplied>αγχνίαν</corr><sic>ευσπαγ<g type="apostrophe"/>χνι<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ν</supplied></sic></choice> 

    <lb n="32"/>καὶ τὴν στοργὴν τῆς ὑμῶν πατριότητος. 
</ab></div><div n="v" org="uniform" part="N" sample="complete" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="33"/>γράφω <choice><corr>σοι</corr><sic>σε</sic></choice> οὖν, ἄδελφε Παι<g type="apostrophe"/>ηου<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς </supplied><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

